ce:section.ce:para:
The practical applicability of the proposed immunosensor for HE4 and HO-8910 cells detection was evaluated in serum samples using the standard addition method. The recovery values of HE4 and HO-8910 cells in serum samples were in an acceptable range of 94.0%–102.0% and 90.7%–102.4%, respectively (Table 1
                         and Table 2
                        ), implying that the proposed immunosensor have a great potential for application in clinical analysis.
